name: asr
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "asr" %}
{% set version = "0.4.1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/asr-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 4fec71291eab856d006df3b54cb21a92d2e418d78d597d243fd5d8dafebb056c

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  entry_points:
    - asr=asr.core.cli:cli
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.5
  run:
    - ase
    - click >=7.0
    - flask
    - matplotlib-base
    - phonopy
    - plotly
    - pymatgen
    - python >=3.5
    - spglib

test:
  imports:
    - asr
    - asr.calculators
  commands:
    - pip check
    - asr --help
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://asr.readthedocs.io/
  license: GPL-3.0-or-later
  license_family: GPL
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Atomic Simulation Recipes'
  description: |
    Recipes for calculating material properties
  doc_url: https://asr.readthedocs.io/
  dev_url: https://gitlab.com/asr-dev/asr

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jan-janssen
